     aircrack-ng.org (http://www.aircrack-ng.org/))

   • Linux kernel with mac80211 stack, introduced in 2.6.22, tested with
     2.6.35 and 2.6.38

   • Wlantools to create the a monitor interface, tested with airmon-ng
     of the aircrack-ng package


